Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:51.51,main,Fuego,0000,0000,0000,,Just Woke Up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:54.25,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Fuegoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.56,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:22:59.01,main,Fuego,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I must do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:22:59.81,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:01.71,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:06.42,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A man who will not allow a single tangle\N to remain! That is Fuegoleon Vermillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:09.53,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think your bedhead is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:12.53,main,Fuego,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there is something I must do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:13.57,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.57,0:23:15.50,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:18.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A man who will make sure every \Nlast tooth is as white as can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:20.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That is Fuegoleon Vermillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.13,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think you've brushed them enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:26.50,main,Fuego,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there is something I must do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.17,main,Fuego,0000,0000,0000,,Just five more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.49,main,both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:34.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A charming man who always goes back \Nto sleep! That is Fuegoleon Vermillioâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:37.53,main,Fuego,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow any more blasphemy \Nagainst me for the sake of jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:44.40,main,Fuego,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Captain of the Crimson \NLion Kings, Fuegoleon Vermillion!
